      • withoutPurge

        public Dispatcher withoutPurge()
        Disables purge(DispatcherPurgeProperties, JobContext) functionality. Avoids additional columns in database needed for purge functionality. Additionally disables resetting failureLimit on unpend.

      • withoutRemaining

        public Dispatcher withoutRemaining()
        Disables Dispatcher.Run.getRemaining() and Dispatcher.Run.getLimit() fields. Avoids additional columns in database.
